,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T19:51:26.000Z","msg":"見到有人教水陷阱但我好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 萬一瞓醒成盤我咪含柒"},{"pid":"860d776d396fb73f1e811701b4822af2959b8d5f","tid":2043552,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T19:52:25.000Z","msg":"好撚驚但真係唔想做家務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多嘢都好憎 突然之間爆出嚟咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa61343a140d66bc1fc410f66f5bef071045fca0","tid":2043552,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T19:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好煩...最主要嘅煩煩到唔想煩連打出嚟都唔想 唉"},{"pid":"96338e0d628ae1066e9b608090264b3c59f2192c","tid":2043552,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T19:54:44.000Z","msg":"我覺得個反應好撚侮辱"},{"pid":"5acddda584b47da330235f677cc84d2bec501f84","tid":2043552,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T19:56:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾app又白邊又要一個一個撳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廢"},{"pid":"107bdbb8cdbb49d39125a41ad390d17c3e10b337","tid":2043552,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T19:58:12.000Z","msg":"之後到講個身同個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇聽過耳濡目染 留喺咁撚品格低劣嘅人身邊係會對自己造成影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc584e3b9829f138c940a04c9a0aaff52af102c","tid":2043552,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T20:02:02.000Z","msg":"其實嚴格嚟講唔關我身邊人事 但對得太多導致好易學撚曬個閪格 所以呢樣令我好撚反感 出污泥不染係好撚難<br />\n我唔想自己變到好似呢啲咁又乞人憎又成個臭閪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但本性淋又覺得好撚心理唔平衡 導致好想直接黑化比佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死臭閪 我可以閪過你<br />\n<br />\n但呢啲心態變換又令我覺得自己咁唔係自己 又會不經意對咗身邊好嘅人閪<br />\n<br />\n但唔轉換心境又好撚谷住 你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9266f6a9b064659d68138b57116b053c8ab10e8d","tid":2043552,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T20:04:40.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗緊直接唔撚忍應該要準備啲乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n到時鬧番佢又會唔會口窒<br />\n<br />\n老實講本錢一定有 只係掙扎個位係我唔想自我否定<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實唔係我問題 如果得我一個咁覺得我都會懷疑同質疑自己<br />\n<br />\n但事實唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問題好撚明顯喺件老臭閪度"},{"pid":"72c0db8ff473a94df7bb5ad96d438bea72358e79","tid":2043552,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T20:05:22.000Z","msg":"真係老臭閪嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又老 格又臭 又閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490d4692591dcde05b267a9818f851fbf1e9493b","tid":2043552,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T20:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259002cb5bd1286acdfab30d113797df5e2dc5bb","tid":2043552,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T20:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e079eb74981f01bcde227a19602434d341262cc7","tid":2043552,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T20:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c57c602f006af47667f29410e9188e4f8187dbc","tid":2043552,"uid":238801,"like":0,"disli